&lt;li&gt;Create, track, and dynamically update detailed Gantt charts across multiple concurrent programs. Visually map out critical paths, resource dependencies, and milestone delivery dates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with the Alliance Manager to monitor project health. Proactively identify risks, timeline variances, resource bottlenecks, or potential delays, providing data-driven updates to support partner communications&lt;/li&gt;
