&lt;li&gt;Capable of reviewing scientific contracts, research plans, and SOWs, successfully translating them into day-to-day operational project plans and timelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent cross-functional communication and stakeholder management skills across diverse technical domains. Ability to lead through influence and coordinate work across teams without direct authority&lt;/li&gt;
