&lt;li&gt;Leverage massive-scale protein and nucleic acid data to train specialized models for protein understanding and design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curate relevant datasets and design tasks for rigorous evaluation of generative models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate across the machine learning and protein design teams to adapt and apply techniques for experimental validation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement, analyze, and interpret multiple computational approaches and present results to colleagues in regular update meetings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work within a collaborative, fast-paced, interdisciplinary team across biology and machine learning to help shape the scientific and strategic vision of the company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
