&lt;li&gt;Experience with conceiving of, implementing, and evaluating novel machine learning techniques at the intersection with biology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Publications at major machine learning conferences (NeurIPS, ICML, ICLR) or scientific journals (Nature, Science, Nature Biotech, Nature Methods, PNAS)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with modern deep learning frameworks such as Pytorch or Jax&lt;/li&gt;
