&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High-growth opportunity with meaningful impact on the future of protein design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive compensation package with equity participation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401(k) with a strong employer match&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;

